    <h1>Behavioral Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">Targeting people by what they do — not who they are. Campaigns built on behavioural signals convert <strong>3-5x better</strong> than demographic-only campaigns and 91% of consumers now expect them.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
